About.Hours & facilities: Open by appointment. Reference assistance available in person and by telephone. Copying services for original records to A3 and photographs.

About.Acquisition focus: To preserve the School's archival records and to acquire memorabilia from ex-students. (90% in-house).

About.Major holdings: North Sydney Girls' High School: Admission registers, photographs, miscellaneous school records and school magazines 1914 to date (20m).
